{"tid":564447,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地產Smart Lady：愛情失意　激發Candy搵銀動力","createTime":"2018-02-18T04:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T02:58:17.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccad31f1574137a485b0e8b41f8b58c0c6924574","tid":564447,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_01b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=1cf554db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_02b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=44ebfdf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_03b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_03b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=c5ce98d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_04b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_04b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=f4d6afa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_05b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_05b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=75f3ca84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_06b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_06b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=2ded63ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_07b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_07b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=acc8068b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/photo/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_08b.jpg?20180214194244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001_08b.jpg%3F20180214194244&h=4fdd0d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n笑容甜美的Candy原是美容師，愛玩非主流音樂，業餘夾Band 4年，會作詞、懂編曲，喜穿短裙及長靴，拿着Keyboard在街頭、酒吧表演，夠Cool又夠型。一年半前，她毅然轉行做地產代理，緣於與拍拖4年、近乎談婚論嫁的男朋友分手而起。<br />\n<br />\n感情受挫，愛情失意，令她不再奢求夢幻愛情，「的起心肝」為事業打拼。於是，她放棄資深美容師的穩定收入，轉職地產代理行業；目標3年內上車，以報答相依為命的媽媽。<br />\n<br />\nCandy「不怕有樓在手會趕客」，反而覺得「有麵包可更放手追求愛情」。由情場轉戰職場、展開人生新一頁的她笑言入行「相逢恨晚」。樓市知識令她大開眼界，轉行是完全正確的選擇，已視為終身職業。<br />\n<br />\n入行一年半，她現時已是美聯首席高級客戶經理，職位為營業員級別中的次高；而加入新公司半年，營業額已達100萬港元，現時年薪約50萬元。<br />\n<br />\n生於單親家庭，她希望為媽媽覓得更好的居住環境，目標在自小長大的葵芳區一帶買兩房單位。為努力儲錢，每次出糧，都會將佣金收入的1/4儲起。為自我激勵，更買了個「金元寶」放在家中作為推動力，期望加快賺錢速度。<br />\n<br />\n她說，轉行後才發現世界很大，之前做美容師，放假超過1星期並不容易，所以只能去日本及泰國等短途旅行，一年會去幾次。現時工作時間彈性，才有機會衝出亞洲去歐洲遊歷，見識世界兼「叉電」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180213%2Fbkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001.html&d=ePnc8nuz0lVNRm5%2BXZzth%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=e3f2f7dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180213/bkn-20180213114350329-0213_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"016a251f5c793748a66b55d1826e111dc1934a58","tid":564447,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"好大波，可否渣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c32393a4cfc9735158e7c933ec6d2e08ae72fdb","tid":564447,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"又唔夠人做aa"},{"pid":"510d8fa885f2d0591fbe609fc21e1e013449ec2a","tid":564447,"uid":163916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"出太陽就要晒床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036df658e4224eefbee07991c1fe28e0e1bbf454","tid":564447,"uid":41944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"買樓送幾q?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1bcb1e30a3248965d24b387fe2737e3520be69","tid":564447,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫Dorina"},{"pid":"a3dd32c1b81a76b05eb85c57a0c143e639742a13","tid":564447,"uid":59100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"咁唔掂點開床單"},{"pid":"468ce3cf2a26d5d2fc3482fc9d4c7b3b092e710c","tid":564447,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acf39bee30051480e6c91107a2494245166125a","tid":564447,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfc2b70af0b06a2370d4357472bed43035e847d9","tid":564447,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike